data.description: This is country living at its finest!  This beautiful Ranchette is located on a quiet county road approx. 4 miles west of Weiser, close to everything outdoor. The home is single level with an open concept kitchen, dining and living room. Engineered hardwood floors have been added throughout much of the home.  Enjoy the split floor plan design with office, bonus room, updated master bath with cultured marble shower surround. The newly remodeled main bath sets off of the large laundry room and leads the the 3 additional bedrooms. The pellet stove insert adds additional heat and ambiance to the home and is surrounded by a rock hearth. French doors lead to the private, covered back patio and the large backyard. The fenced, irrigated pasture is just waiting for animals! Barn, paved driveway, underground sprinklers, and detached pass through garage. Fruit trees, garden space, and mature landscaping.
